	You await the arrival of the get-away van which is supposed to be transporting two
	fellow gangsters. Under some careful instruction each of you is required to carry out a
	unique part in the mission. This mission being for the Joker however you, of course, have 
	been told nothing about your accomplices. 
	
	Your job is relatively simple.
	
		Step 1 - Get to the bank
		Step 2 - Find a way to hold the bank clerks and clients hostage while the safe is infiltrated
		Step 3 - Load up the get-away vehicle with the stolen money
		Step 4 - Escape the bank undetected